  "title": "A gray cigar-shaped UFO spotted in Curitiba [1998]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/19/a-gray-cigar-shaped-ufo-spotted-in-curitiba-1998/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-vk",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>AUG 29th, 1998</strong>. Time: 20h30 pm. Duration:  not determined. In the city of Curitiba, State of Paraná, a person residing in the Xaxim neighborhood spotted an unidentified flying object in an elongated shape and gray color. The witness was not able to estimate the altitude or the speed of the UFO, which, according to her report, headed for the North direction coming from the South. The sighting was carried out on a clear night with good visibility, with no markings or trails of condensation left on the object&#8217;s trajectory.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.527. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre a ocorrência de objeto voador não identificado na região de Curitiba, Paraná”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
  "excerpt": "<p>AUG 29th, 1998. Time: 20h30 pm. Duration:  not determined. In the city of Curitiba, State of Paraná, a person residing in the Xaxim neighborhood spotted an unidentified flying object in an elongated shape and gray color. The witness was not able to estimate the altitude or the speed of the UFO, which, according to her [&hellip;]</p>\n",
